The value set is based on a subset of the code list from the SOR lookup table 'SOR-Enhedstyper' (http://sor.sundhedsstyrelsen.dsdn.dk/lookupdata/#EntityTypes, accessable on Sundhedsdatanettet (SDN)), which is based on SNOMED codes.
